title: Ep. #61 | Catching Up: Yubin (BONUS)
description:
K-pop veteran Yubin is here to discuss her new music and company rrr Entertainment! She reflects on the challenges and joys of being a CEO, JYP's advice on running a successful business, and her experience touring overseas with the Wonder Girls.


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.
